{"tid":2170044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯一公務員被發現死亡 生前曾與極權對抗 拒認選舉結果","createTime":"2020-08-23T03:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T12:44:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4647e8c88184ef76b31b348d53f36acd4a93af1","tid":2170044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:47:47.000Z","msg":"加山傳播 DB Channel<br />\n<br />\n白羅斯城市Vawkavysk一名軍事博物館總監 Kanstansin Shyshmakou，被發現伏屍河中，得年29歲。他生前曾拒絕簽署不合規格的選舉規程，拒絕承認尋求連任的白羅斯總統Lukashenko 勝出大選。雖然當局稱初步調查顯示死因並與罪案無關，但Shyshmakou 於拒絕簽署的翌日就失蹤，而且調查指他主要死因非自然造成，因此白羅斯內外都認為他慘遭毒手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/?__tn__=%2Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fdbchannel.hk%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cg&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=a24c6efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/?__tn__=%2Cg</a>"},{"pid":"43a766f4ef23708a7cdd099fac09e1dfd5cac38a","tid":2170044,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"文明大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1742b30679753600fbbbc8b63334c19f45991402","tid":2170044,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但願我哋發生過嘅嘢唔好再發生，可惜悲劇重演，人生....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de870c3c3cb75e984a772e0c6ce3c131afb40f07","tid":2170044,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1742b30679753600fbbbc8b63334c19f45991402","tid":2170044,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" 